      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Thomas Petzke</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:207px;\"><a href=\"http://www.fam-petzke.de/contact_en.shtml\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/b/b3/ThomasPetzke.jpg\" width=\"205\" height=\"250\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:ThomasPetzke.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Thomas Petzke <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Thomas Petzke</b>,<br />\na German computer scientist, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Software_architect\">IT architect</a>, \nand as avocational chess programmer author of the chess engine <a href=\"/index.php?title=MACE&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"MACE (page does not exist)\">mACE</a> written in <a href=\"/Pascal\" title=\"Pascal\">Free Pascal</a> with an own <a href=\"/GUI\" title=\"GUI\">GUI</a>, \nand the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant chess engine <a href=\"/ICE\" title=\"ICE\">iCE</a>, written in <a href=\"/Cpp\" title=\"Cpp\">C++</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \nThomas reports the development in his mACE and iCE <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blog\">blog</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>, \nand further maintains a chess programming site <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Thomas_Petzke&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Thomas_Petzke&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=39424\">Newbie question about PVS zws verification</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 19, 2011 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40278\">binary portability between 32bit and 64 bit</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 05, 2011 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=40626\">Does a \"en passent\" aware PGN2EPD converter exist</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 03, 2011 </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=42045\">EPD endgame collection for some 4 and 5 man positions</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 18, 2012</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=42291&amp;start=1\">Re: Moving to Magic Bitboards... any advice?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 03, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Magic_Bitboards\" title=\"Magic Bitboards\">Magic Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=48352\">iCE 1.0 released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 20, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=50823&amp;start=29\">Re: The texel evaluation function optimization algorithm</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 31, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Texel%27s_Tuning_Method\" title=\"Texel&#39;s Tuning Method\">Texel's Tuning Method</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=51811&amp;start=11\">Re: Thoughs on eval terms</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 01, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=54021&amp;start=8\">Re: A little improvement to the Texel's tuning method</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, October 22, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Texel%27s_Tuning_Method\" title=\"Texel&#39;s Tuning Method\">Texel's Tuning Method</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=54337&amp;start=9\">Re: Just another movegen</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 18, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Move_Generation\" title=\"Move Generation\">Move Generation</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Thomas_Petzke&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=54950\">Move Number Indication in PGN Export Format</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 12, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=57225&amp;start=47\">Re: Evaluation Tuning</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 24, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Texel%27s_Tuning_Method\" title=\"Texel&#39;s Tuning Method\">Texel's Tuning Method</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=58800\">iCE 3 gets released</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 04, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=58795&amp;start=1\">Re: Comparison of bitboard attack-getter variants</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 04, 2016&#160;» <a href=\"/Sliding_Piece_Attacks\" title=\"Sliding Piece Attacks\">Sliding Piece Attacks</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=63926&amp;start=9\">Re: Parameter tuning with multi objective optimization</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 10, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69911&amp;start=2\">Re: Any news from Thomas Petzke&#160;?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 15, 2019</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Thomas_Petzke&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fam-petzke.de/chess_home_en.shtml\">Chess Programming - Home</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fam-petzke.de/cp_inside_ice_en.shtml\">Chess Programming - Inside iCE</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://macechess.blogspot.com/\">mACE Chess</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Thomas_Petzke&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fam-petzke.de/contact_en.shtml\">Contact Details www.fam-petzke.de</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://macechess.blogspot.com/2010/08/getting-started.html\">mACE Chess: Getting started</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://macechess.blogspot.com/\">mACE Chess</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.fam-petzke.de/chess_home_en.shtml\">Chess Programming - Home</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Thomas Petzke</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301084843\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.018 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.021 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 79/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 170/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:7232